I made a tiktok video about my PCOS & I’ve been flooded with DMs about how I cleared my skin & deal with my symptoms. I figured it would be easier to just sit down and chat about my whole experience. I didn’t feel it was necessary to make this a whole production with edits so enjoy me rambling on for 10 minutes. I want to be as real as I can with y’all. I will still respond to all the DMs that I can. I hope this helps & please message me with any other questions. If you’re struggling right now, I PROMISE it will get better 💓💞
Thank you to @esthylexi for changing my life & helping me get my skin back! #pcos #pcosawareness #pcosfighter #acnepositivity #skincare #skincaretips
